---
const heroTitleChars = [..."Be a Good Coiner"];
const heroMobileTitleLines = ["Be a Good", "Coiner"];
---

<section class="overflow-hidden bg-[var(--bg-canvas)] pb-0 text-center">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-[1094px] px-6 pt-[52px] md:px-5 md:pt-[67px]">
    <p class="hero-kicker mb-4 text-center text-[18px] font-bold leading-[27px] tracking-[0.08em] text-[var(--text-primary)] md:mb-6 md:text-[26px] md:leading-[39px] md:tracking-[0.04em]">
      トレードを、感覚から仕組みへ。
    </p>

    <h1
      class="mx-auto mb-6 text-center text-[var(--text-primary)] md:mb-6"
      style="font-family: 'Avenir Next', 'Avenir', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif; font-weight: 900; font-kerning: normal;"
    >
      <span class="hidden text-[68px] leading-[68px] tracking-[-0.05em] md:inline-flex md:text-[clamp(60px,7.71vw,111px)] md:leading-[1] md:tracking-[-0.055em]" aria-label="Be a Good Coiner">
        {heroTitleChars.map((char, index) => (
          <span
            class="hero-title-char"
            style={`animation-delay: ${180 + index * 55}ms;`}
            aria-hidden="true"
          >
            {char === " " ? "\u00A0" : char}
          </span>
        ))}
      </span>
      <span class="inline-block text-[68px] leading-[68px] tracking-[-0.05em] md:hidden" aria-label="Be a Good Coiner">
        {heroMobileTitleLines.map((line, lineIndex) => (
          <>
            {[...line].map((char, charIndex) => (
              <span
                class="hero-title-char"
                style={`animation-delay: ${180 + (lineIndex * 10 + charIndex) * 55}ms;`}
                aria-hidden="true"
              >
                {char === " " ? "\u00A0" : char}
              </span>
            ))}
            {lineIndex < heroMobileTitleLines.length - 1 && <br />}
          </>
        ))}
      </span>
    </h1>

    <p
      class="hero-body mx-auto hidden max-w-[760px] text-center text-[18px] font-medium leading-[36px] tracking-[0.04em] text-[var(--text-secondary)] md:block"
      style="font-family: 'Inter', 'Noto Sans JP', sans-serif;"
    >
      グッドコイナーは、感覚や感情に左右されず、<br />
      明確なルールと目的に基づいて暗号資産を売買するトレード管理アプリです。<br />
      「Be a Good Coiner」を合言葉に、再現性のあるトレードを優しくサポートします。
    </p>
    <p
      class="hero-body mx-auto max-w-[345px] text-center text-[14px] font-normal leading-[1.9] tracking-[0.04em] text-[var(--text-heading-card)] md:hidden"
      style="font-family: 'Inter', 'Noto Sans JP', sans-serif;"
    >
      グッドコイナーは、感覚や感情に左右されず、<br />
      明確なルールと目的に基づいて暗号資産を売買する<br />
      トレード管理アプリです。
    </p>

    <div class="hero-cta mx-auto mt-6 flex w-full max-w-[345px] flex-col items-center gap-4 md:mt-9 md:w-80 md:gap-5">
      <a
        id="download"
        href="#"
        class="inline-flex h-[60px] w-full max-w-[262px] items-center justify-center gap-2.5 whitespace-nowrap rounded-[var(--radius-pill)] bg-[var(--accent-yellow)] px-8 py-4 text-[16px] font-bold leading-none tracking-[0.01em] text-[var(--text-primary)] transition hover:bg-[var(--accent-yellow-hover)] md:h-auto md:max-w-none md:text-[18px] md:leading-[32.38px]"
      >
        <img
          src="/assets/icons/Finder_Icon_macOS.png"
          alt=""
          aria-hidden="true"
          class="h-7 w-7"
        />
        Mac版をダウンロード
      </a>
      <p class="text-center text-[12px] font-normal leading-[1.3] tracking-[0.04em] text-[var(--text-tertiary)] md:whitespace-nowrap md:leading-[12px]">
        ※現在GMOコインユーザーのみ利用可能。<br class="md:hidden" />
        順次拡張予定です。
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="hero-video-wrap mx-auto mt-12 max-w-[1320px] px-6 md:mt-14 md:px-6">
    <div class="mx-auto rounded-[14px] border-[4px] border-[#eeeeee] bg-[#eeeeee] md:max-w-none md:rounded-[var(--radius-panel)] md:border-[14px]">
      <div class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-[10px] bg-[#eeeeee] md:rounded-[34px]">
        <video
          src="/dashboard.mp4"
          autoplay
          muted
          loop
          playsinline
          class="block h-auto w-full"
        ></video>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .hero-kicker {
    display: inline-block;
    white-space: nowrap;
    animation: hero-kicker-reveal 0.48s cubic-bezier(0.2, 0.8, 0.2, 1) 0.05s both;
    transform-origin: left center;
  }

  .hero-title-char {
    display: inline-block;
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(18px) scaleY(0.92) rotate(-4deg);
    animation: hero-char-wave 0.62s cubic-bezier(0.2, 0.75, 0.2, 1) both;
    will-change: transform, opacity;
  }

  .hero-body {
    opacity: 0;
    animation: hero-kicker-reveal 0.56s cubic-bezier(0.2, 0.8, 0.2, 1) 0.78s both;
  }

  .hero-cta {
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(14px);
    animation: hero-cta-reveal 0.42s cubic-bezier(0.22, 0.8, 0.2, 1) 1.32s both;
  }

  .hero-video-wrap {
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(18px) scale(0.985);
    animation: hero-video-reveal 0.62s cubic-bezier(0.2, 0.82, 0.2, 1) 1.62s both;
  }

  @keyframes hero-kicker-reveal {
    0% {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateX(-28px);
      clip-path: inset(0 100% 0 0);
    }

    100% {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateX(0);
      clip-path: inset(0 0 0 0);
    }
  }

  @keyframes hero-char-wave {
    0% {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(18px) scaleY(0.92) rotate(-4deg);
    }

    55% {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(-10px) scaleY(1.04) rotate(1deg);
    }

    100% {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0) scaleY(1) rotate(0deg);
    }
  }

  @keyframes hero-cta-reveal {
    from {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(14px);
    }

    to {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }
  }

  @keyframes hero-video-reveal {
    0% {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(18px) scale(0.985);
      filter: blur(8px);
    }

    100% {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0) scale(1);
      filter: blur(0);
    }
  }

  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
    .hero-kicker,
    .hero-title-char,
    .hero-body,
    .hero-cta,
    .hero-video-wrap {
      animation: none;
      opacity: 1;
      transform: none;
      filter: none;
    }
  }
</style>
